DESCRIPTION :
-------------

This software performs stochastic optimisation on deterministic functions. 

A C code implementation of PISAA for minimising any R-valued cost function 
of a R^n-valued variable.

The Rastrigin's (cost) function is included.

Karagiannis, G., Konomi, B., Lin, G., & Liang F. (under revision). 
Parallel and Interacting Stochastic Approximation Annealing algorithms 
for global optimisation.

Copyright 2014 Georgios Karagiannis

